'''Lúthien''' can refer to:
*[[Lúthien]], a heroine of the [[First Age]] and the daughter of [[Thingol]] and [[Melian]] the [[Maiar|Maia]].
*[[Lúthien (son of Gelmir)|Lúthien]], a [[Gnome]] in a prose fragment following ''[[The Book of Lost Tales]]''.
*[[Lúthien (son of Telimektar)|Lúthien]], a [[Valar|Vala]], the son of [[Telimektar]] in ''The Book of Lost Tales''.
*[[Ælfwine|Lúthien]], a name given to [[Ælfwine]] by the [[Elves]] in ''The Book of Lost Tales''.
*[[Luthany|Lúthien]], a name for [[wikipedia:England|England]] in ''The Book of Lost Tales''.
*[[Hendwine|Lúthien]], a [[Gnomish]] name for Hendwine, a son of [[Eriol]] in a text associated with ''The Book of Lost Tales''.
